"audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10315,"position":3,"arabic":"نَقْعُدُ","translation":"আমরা বসতাম","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10316,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْهَا","translation":"সেখানে","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10317,"position":5,"arabic":"مَقَـٰعِدَ","translation":"আসনগুলোতে","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10318,"position":6,"arabic":"لِلسَّمْعِ ۖ","translation":"শুনার জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10320,"position":7,"arabic":"فَمَن","translation":"যে কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10321,"position":8,"arabic":"يَسْتَمِعِ","translation":"শুনবে","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10322,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔانَ","translation":"এখন","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10323,"position":10,"arabic":"يَجِدْ","translation":"সে পাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10324,"position":11,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"তার জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10325,"position":12,"arabic":"شِهَابًۭا","translation":"অগ্নিশিখা","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10326,"position":13,"arabic":"رَّصَدًۭا","translation":"পেতে রাখা","audioUrl":"wbw/072_009_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10327,"position":14,"arabic":"٩","translation":"(৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":10,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا لَا نَدْرِىٓ أَشَرٌّ أُرِيدَ بِمَن فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ أَمْ أَرَادَ بِهِمْ رَبُّهُمْ رَشَدًۭا","translation":"\"'And [now we have become aware] that we [created beings] may not know whether evil fortune is intended for [any of] those who live on earth, or whether it is their Sustainer’s will to endow them with consciousness of what is right:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5457.mp3","surahId":7